  "title": "Front Desk / Reception",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Handle customer appointments, calls and register new customers</li>\n  <li>Process transactions on the checked out computer system</li>\n  <li>Provide customers with high-quality customer service and treatment suggestions</li>\n  <li>Establish relationships with existing and new customers to maximize sales opportunities</li>\n  <li>Handle customer questions and feedback</li>\n  <li>Provide professional consultation and customer needs assessment</li>\n  <li>Follow up inquiries about customers' treatment methods and purchased products</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job Requirements</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Experienced in reception service</li>\n  <li>On-job training provided</li>\n  <li>Good communication skills and willing to learn</li>\n  <li>Basic computer knowledge and skills</li>\n</ul>",
